author: cmpilato
msg: Finish issue #964.
* subversion/include/svn_client.h
(svn_client_get_commit_log_t): Add 'tmp_file' param.
* subversion/clients/cmdline/cl.h
(svn_cl__get_log_message): Add 'tmp_file' param.
* subversion/clients/cmdline/util.c
(svn_cl__edit_externally): Leave a TODO reference to issue #929.
(svn_cl__get_log_message): Add 'tmp_file' param, and shadow
lmb->tmpfile_left's value throughout the function in it.  Also, if
a commit item's path is empty, print '.' instead.
* subversion/libsvn_client/commit.c
(import, import_dir): Add 'excludes' argument.
(svn_client_import): Update call to log_msg_func, and stuff any
tmpfiles into the excludes hash.  Update calls to import and import_dir.
(svn_client_commit): Update call to log_msg_func, ignore any tmpfiles.
* subversion/libsvn_client/add.c
(svn_client_mkdir): Update call to log_msg_func, ignore any tmpfiles.
* subversion/libsvn_client/copy.c
(setup_copy): Update call to log_msg_func, ignore any tmpfiles.
* subversion/libsvn_client/delete.c
(svn_client_delete): Update call to log_msg_func, ignore any tmpfiles.
